さい。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/35", "sentence": ["…象について伺っております。これは、自国に対する攻撃の抑止なのか、それとも同盟国への攻撃の抑止を含めて考えていらっしゃるのか、お答えください。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/38", "sentence": ["○田島麻衣子君答えられないのかという声が隣から上がっておりますが、新三要件に合致する範囲で同盟国への抑止も含むという点でよろしいですか。"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/40", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/42", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/44", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/46", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/48", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/50", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/52", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/54", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/56", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/58", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/60", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/62", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/64", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/66", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/68", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/70", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/72", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120815261X01520220318/74", "sentence": []}]}]}]